body_html:
The relevant error is in this log: https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/pytorch-builds/job/pytorch-win-ws2016-cuda9-cudnn7-py3-test2/1711/console:

"CHECK failed: file != NULL"

This is an error being thrown by the protobuf library. It only occurs on windows, OS X and Linux work fine. It is illustrative of our problems using protobuf to remove nanopb.
